@startuml Product_Management_Sequence
autonumber

skinparam BoxPadding 10
skinparam ParticipantPadding 10
skinparam defaultFontSize 20
skinparam maxMessageSize 400

actor "Admin Sistem" as Admin
boundary "UI Produk" as UI
control "Product Controller" as Controller
database "DB" as DB

== 1. Pengambilan Data ==
Admin -> UI : Buka list produk (Cari/Filter)
UI -> Controller : Ambil daftar produk
Controller -> DB : Query data produk & varian aktif
DB --> UI : List Produk & Detail Stok

== 2. Tambah Produk Baru ==
Admin -> UI : Input data produk & multi-varian
UI -> Controller : Simpan data produk baru
activate Controller
Controller -> DB : Simpan data produk, varian, & HPP awal
DB --> UI : Konfirmasi Berhasil Simpan
deactivate Controller

== 3. Update & Soft Delete ==
Admin -> UI : Edit data atau Delete
alt Aksi: Edit Produk
    UI -> Controller : Perbarui data produk
    activate Controller
    Controller -> Controller : Validasi & Cek HPP sebelumnya
    Controller -> DB : Perbarui data produk & Hitung ulang Average Cost (HPP)
    deactivate Controller
else Aksi: Hapus Produk
    UI -> Controller : Request penghapusan produk
    Controller -> DB : Ubah status produk menjadi tidak aktif (Soft Delete)
end
Controller --> UI : Konfirmasi Berhasil

@enduml